Quickstrike:







Seeing the bots burst in, Quickstrike leapt from the control chair, but got 
hit on the side of his chest and his leg by two of them. He landed hard on 
the floor. He tried to run, but his leg gave out. He could only drag/limp 
his way to safety. He threw himself to the side of a computer.
He knew he was one dead bot.
